headline: MetLife Investment Management Names Geert Henckens Global Head of Private Fixed Income
summary: WHIPPANY, N.J., August 21, 2025--MetLife Investment Management (MIM), the institutional asset management business of MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET), today announced that it has named Geert Henckens global head of Private Fixed Income.
